About Me

My name is Tiffany. I have a corgi named Gizmo. He is named after the cute gremlin from the movie Gremlins because of his big ears, but he can sometimes be a little gremlin.

On the weekends, I love to play tennis with friends. I'm a little rusty, but I am hoping to improve over the summer. In addition to tennis, I love to play the ukulele and cook. I make a delicious carbonara and pork adobo.

Lastly, I am a total Disney and Star Wars nerd. A goal of mine is to visit all the Disneylands to ride all the rides and eat all the themed food. You can always find me doing coding projects or coming up with a plan for my next trip to Disneyland.

) } export default About;
